						               													<description>The deckbuilding battle for all creation!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You and your opponents start with identical decks of low-level angels.  Each turn, you will have the opportunity to purchase cards to add to your deck.  Angels&amp;hellip;will form your &amp;ldquo;host&amp;rdquo; army.  Demons&amp;hellip;will oppose the actions of your opponent&amp;rsquo;s host.  Relics can be attached to angels, making them more powerful.  Humans&amp;hellip;can also be added to your host and your horde, granting group bonuses.  And miracles, bring incredible powers into play each time they are drawn.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Build your host&amp;hellip;and when you have enough points, challenge one of the three locations in play.  If your host is strong enough and can survive a horde challenge from your opponent, the location will be yours.  The harder the location&amp;hellip;the greater the rewards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Once three locations have been won by either player, it is time for the final battle.  You&amp;rsquo;ll examine the rewards granted by conquered locations:  They will allow you to add a certain number of angels and demons to your final army.  You&amp;rsquo;ll search your deck, pull your rewards, form your army&amp;hellip;and compare against your opponent.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Greatest power among final armies wins all!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
